            <Title>SONSHIP - GOD THE SUPREME</Title>
            <Text>GOD THE SUPREME - SONSHIP

God the Supreme is the God of time and space. He is evolving but it is important to remember there will come a time when God the Supreme will be complete. There will be no need for time since all potentials will be exhausted in time. The seven super universes will be settled in light and life and The Almighty Supreme will flash into existence all at once. 
At that moment we will all simultaneously discover God the Almighty Supreme. This is also the concept spoken of in CIM-OE when referring to the Sonship. To understand the course’s perspective on Sonship and time it is important to understand the Urantia books concept of God the Supreme and our part in it. They both say the same thing. To us time seems to be our only reality. But time and space are just mechanisms designed to limit our free will response until we mature as a culture. Our minds have the power to discover spirit and identify with that spirit now. Our culture and our beliefs about time hold us back. Jesus gave us his course to help us identity with spirit reality now if we choose. He is telling Helen about God the Supreme only he refers to it as the Sonship. It is a top down perspective, a fatherly perspective of the whole. To perceive everyone as part of God the Supreme and an integral part of him is a fatherly perspective. The goal of the Supreme is the goal of the individual. The values of the Supreme are our potential eternal values. Jesus goal is to get his creation settled in light and life and eventually to become part of The Almighty Supreme. I’ve listed a few comparisons below.   
 
Each of us personally adds one more degree to the Sonship or God the Supreme. We are each an integral part of the whole Sonship. 
 
CIM-OE quote:  “If all the Souls God created are His Sons, then every soul must be an integral part of the whole Sonship.  

Urantia quote: Page 1287 Paragraph 4 (117:0.4) “when an ascending mortal personality finally attunes to the divine leading of the indwelling Adjuster, then has the actuality of the Supreme become real by one more degree in the universes; then has the divinity of supremacy advanced one more step toward cosmic realization.” 
 
Jesus describes the Sonship as the sum of all souls created by God. The Urantia book describes the Supreme as the sum total of all finite growth or the synthetic cumulative total.  

CIM-OE quote: “Miracles make Souls one in Christ. They depend on cooperation because the Sonship is the sum of all the souls God created.” 

Urantia quote: “The far-flung diversification of eternal energy, divine spirit, and universal mind attains finite culmination in the evolution of the Supreme, who is the sum total of all finite growth,” 

Urantia quote: “The parts and individuals of the grand universe evolve as a reflection of the total evolution of the Supreme, while in turn the Supreme is the synthetic cumulative total of all grand universe evolution.” 
 
The Urantia book says we will only know GOD THE SUPREME when we all simultaneously discover him together. CIM-OE says the Sonship will not be complete until all the parts of the Sonship have returned.  

CIM-OE quote: “The Sonship in its oneness does transcend the sum of its parts. However, this is obscured as long as any of its parts are missing. That is why the conflict cannot ultimately be resolved until all the parts of the Sonship have returned. Only then can the meaning of wholeness, in the true sense, be fully understood.” 

CIM-OE quote: “Your brother is the mirror in which you will see the image of yourself as long as perception lasts. And perception will last until the Sonship knows itself as whole. 

Urantia quote: “God the Father can be found by any individual who has attained the divine level of Godlikeness, but God the Supreme will never be personally discovered by any one creature until that far-distant time when, through the universal attainment of perfection, all creatures will simultaneously find him.” 

Urantia quote: “But no single ascender will ever find the Supreme until all ascenders have reached that maximum universe maturity which qualifies them simultaneously to participate in this discovery.” 
 
The Urantia book says the growth of God the Supreme will come to an end and with it an end to creature evolution. We will have exhausted all potential in time and space. CIM-OE says time is a teaching device and will end when learning is complete. 
 
CIM-OE quote: “The purpose of time is to enable man to learn to use it constructively. Time is thus a teaching device and a means to an end. It will cease when it is no longer useful in facilitating learning.” 

CIM-OE quote: “What is the face of Christ but his who went a moment into timelessness and brought a clear reflection of the unity he felt an instant back to bless the world?” 

CIM-OE quote: “So do the parts of God's Son gradually join in time, and with each joining is the end of time brought nearer.” 

